  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MuTA59">
<l>vāḻum vakaiyaṟintēṉ maipō ṉeṭuvaraivāy</l>
<l>tāḻu maruvipōṟ ṟārkiṭappa – cūḻun</l>
<l>tirumā maṇivaṇṇaṉ ceṅkaṇmā leṅkaḷ</l>
<l>perumā ṉaṭicērap peṟṟu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I have understood a way of living</l>
<l>– after having gotten to join the feet of our great lord,</l>
<l>red-eyed Māl, the one of great sapphire colour, with Śrī who enfolds</l>
<l>[him] so that she lies as a garland, like a waterfall that comes down</l>
<l>	from a high mountain [dark] as kajal.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
